---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Sarah J Mercer
description: Build your own tools with AI. No tech background needed.
---

{% set featured = collections.posts | reverse | first %}

<div class="hero">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">We Can Build</p>
    <h1>Build your own tools with AI.</h1>
    <p>I'm Sarah. I'm not a developer. My husband got me over the first hurdle, and now I build and ship everything in my startup myself. I'll teach you to do the same, one small tool at a time. No tech background needed.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      {% if featured %}<a class="btn" href="{{ featured.url }}">Read the first post</a>{% endif %}
      <a class="btn ghost" href="/tutorials/">See what's coming</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="portrait">[ your photo ]</div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="sec-head"><h2>Start here</h2><a href="/tutorials/">All tutorials &rarr;</a></div>
  {% if featured %}
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="ph">
      {% if featured.data.cover %}
        <img src="{{ featured.data.cover }}" alt="{{ featured.data.title }}" />
      {% else %}
        [ cover image ]
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="tag">New</span>
      <h3>{{ featured.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ featured.data.summary }}</p>
      <a class="btn" href="{{ featured.url }}">Read the post</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-head"><h2>Ideas I'm chewing on</h2></div>
  <p style="color:#54585f;font-size:16px;margin:0 0 18px;max-width:640px;">Honest truth: I haven't fully decided what the series will look like yet. These are some of the things on my list. They might all happen, they might not, and the order will almost certainly shift.</p>
  <div class="grid3">
    <div class="card idea"><p class="k">Maybe first</p><h4>A timeline generator</h4><p>Turn a list of dates into a clean visual timeline. Could be a friendly first build.</p></div>
    <div class="card idea"><p class="k">Maybe</p><h4>How software actually runs</h4><p>The scary-sounding bits, explained in plain English. No jargon left behind.</p></div>
    <div class="card idea"><p class="k">The big one, maybe</p><h4>A passive time recorder</h4><p>The tool that got me hooked on building. Whether it's the right fit for a beginners' series, I'm still working out.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-head"><h2>Just want to use the tools?</h2></div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="ph"><img src="/assets/images/nimble-tech-logo.svg" alt="Nimble Tech" /></div>
    <div>
      <span class="tag">Nimble Tech</span>
      <h3>Don't want to build things yourself? Check out Nimble Tech's library of tools.</h3>
      <p>I run Nimble Tech alongside this. It's where the tools I've finished and polished actually live, ready to use straight away. Built mostly for lawyers and the firms they work in, all aimed at taking the dull bits off your plate.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="https://nimbletech.uk">Visit Nimble Tech &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="band" id="signup">
  <h3>Want each tutorial in your inbox?</h3>
  <p>One short email when a new build-along goes live. No spam, no jargon.</p>
  <form class="form" name="newsletter" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="newsletter" />
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@email.com" aria-label="Email address" required />
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
  </form>
</div>
